    <h1>About Me</h1>
	<p>My name is Alejandro Lopez and as of Spring 2026 I am a Freshman at Oklahoma State University. I was born and raised in Oklahoma (unfortunately), and I want to be able to make a new life for myself. I hope that through my college education, the friends I make, and the personal journey I'm on that I can make it all happen.<br>You can also just call me Alex or Jandro. </p>
	<p>I was born on June 1st, 2006 in Woodward, Oklahoma and was raised in a small town called Shattuck. I'll be honest, barely ANYTHING interesting of note happens from that point on until college, and if there was, it's not pretty.</p>

	<p>What you do need to know is that I fought hard to be able for a chance at being here and making a life that I want to live. I've been able to do just that. I've been able to make so many new friends, memories, and learn so much, and I want to go even farther.</p>

	<h2>Fun Facts about Me/Trivia</h2>
	<p>*I'm Valedictorian for my high school class</p>
	<p>*I love hats and keychains, and I like to collect both whenever I go somewhere new</p>
	<p>*I'm secretly fond of plushies</p>
	<p>*I won first place in the 2025 Poketoberfest Root Beer Chugging Contest</p>
	<p>*If I was born 5 days later I'd be born on 6/6/6. Scary!</p>
	<p>*My favorite holidays are Halloween and Christmas</p>
	<p>*I've been told I'm a very good cook</p>
	<p>*</p>
